This project is built from the professor's Assignment 1.04 solution.
The codes for this project are written in "poke327.c".

In this program, user can move the PC around based on the corresponding keys. 
If the PC is on top of a Pokemart/ Pokemon Center, user can enter and exit the buildings.
User can also see the list of trainers and scroll through the list if it does not fit everything in the screen.
User can use the escape key to quit a battle or return from the list of trainers.
When the PC met a NPC, it will go into a Pokemon battle.